        "TileImage": "$($repository 241054ef-325f-4c66-94f6-442d78f591a6).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening, agent.\r\rA small cell of would-be bioterrorists have infiltrated Sapienza, disguised as locals, hoping to steal a chemical weapon before it reaches author Craig Black. While we&apos;ll have to deal with Mr. Black soon, this team has had a contract placed on them, and must be dealt with eventually anyway.\r\rYou are free to handle this situation however you wish, but, as always, it would be preferable if you would do so without collateral damage or being tied to the scene.\r\rGood hunting.",
